dreisoft.tresos.launcher2.api.module

Class ModuleVersion

  • java.lang.Object
    • dreisoft.tresos.launcher2.api.module.ModuleVersion

  • public class ModuleVersion
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents module version information (SpecVersion, RelVersion, SwVersion). A version has the form: [ <prefix> " " ] <major-number> [ "." <minor-number> [ "." <patch-number> ] ] [ " " <suffix> ].

    Copyright (C) Elektrobit Automotive GmbH - All rights reserved

    Since:
    2008.a

      • ModuleVersion

        public ModuleVersion(java.lang.String version)
              throws java.lang.NumberFormatException
        Parses versions in the form [prefix " "+ ] major [ "." minor [ "." patch ] ] [ " "+ suffix ] where major, minor and patch can also be '*'.
        Parameters:
        version - The version to parse
        Throws:
        java.lang.NumberFormatException - in case the version number cannot be parsed
